+/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
+ *
+ * parquet_gsi.c
+ *    Native PostgreSQL support code for the parquet_gsi extension.
+ *
+ * This native implementation currently provides:
+ *   - a background worker that periodically scans a configured directory
+ *   - a SQL-callable scan function for one-off runs
+ *   - worker heartbeat/status bookkeeping in extension-owned tables
+ *   - catalog-backed row-group zonemap lookup helpers
+ *   - an FDW path that prunes candidate files before scanning
+ *
+ * Native row-group-only reads and planner-hook cost integration are still
+ * future work.
+ *
+ *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
+ */
